{
  "video_id": "fWqKalpYgLo",
  "title": "Lessons from a solar storm chaser | Miho Janvier",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13927.0,
      "end_time": 16857.0,
      "text": "It is almost the end of the winter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16881.0,
      "end_time": 19452.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;ve woken up to a cold house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19476.0,
      "end_time": 22872.0,
      "text": "which is weird, because you left the heater on all night."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24124.0,
      "end_time": 25424.0,
      "text": "You turn on the light."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25449.0,
      "end_time": 26699.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not working."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27252.0,
      "end_time": 32519.0,
      "text": "Actually, the coffee maker, the TV -- none of them are working."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33249.0,
      "end_time": 35732.0,
      "text": "Life outside also seems to have stopped."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36796.0,
      "end_time": 38624.0,
      "text": "There are no schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38648.0,
      "end_time": 40889.0,
      "text": "most of the businesses are shut,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40913.0,
      "end_time": 42938.0,
      "text": "and there are no working trains."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43852.0,
      "end_time": 47558.0,
      "text": "This is not the opening scene of a zombie apocalypse movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48332.0,
      "end_time": 54244.0,
      "text": "This is what happened in March 1989 in the Canadian province of Quebec,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54268.0,
      "end_time": 56948.0,
      "text": "when the power grid lost power."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57523.0,
      "end_time": 58686.0,
      "text": "The culprit?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59106.0,
      "end_time": 60304.0,
      "text": "A solar storm."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61551.0,
      "end_time": 64614.0,
      "text": "Solar storms are giant clouds of particles"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64638.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66916.0,
      "text": "escaping from the Sun from time to time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66940.0,
      "end_time": 72289.0,
      "text": "and a constant reminder that we live in the neighborhood of an active star."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73157.0,
      "end_time": 75765.0,
      "text": "And I, as a solar physicist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75789.0,
      "end_time": 79509.0,
      "text": "I have a tremendous chance to study these solar storms."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79533.0,
      "end_time": 82254.0,
      "text": "But you see, \"solar storm chaser\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82278.0,
      "end_time": 83950.0,
      "text": "is not just a cool title."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84799.0,
      "end_time": 88435.0,
      "text": "My research helps to understand where they come from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88459.0,
      "end_time": 89903.0,
      "text": "how they behave"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89927.0,
      "end_time": 91102.0,
      "text": "and, in the long run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91126.0,
      "end_time": 94124.0,
      "text": "aims to mitigate their effects on human societies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94148.0,
      "end_time": 95830.0,
      "text": "which I&#39;ll get to in a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97106.0,
      "end_time": 102649.0,
      "text": "At the beginning of the space exploration age 50 years ago only,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 102674.0,
      "end_time": 104832.0,
      "text": "the probes we sent in space"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104856.0,
      "end_time": 107669.0,
      "text": "revealed that the planets in our Solar System"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107694.0,
      "end_time": 112144.0,
      "text": "constantly bathe in a stream of particles that are coming from the Sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 112168.0,
      "end_time": 114769.0,
      "text": "and that we call the solar wind."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115722.0,
      "end_time": 119339.0,
      "text": "And in the same way that global wind patterns here on Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 119363.0,
      "end_time": 121561.0,
      "text": "can be affected by hurricanes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121585.0,
      "end_time": 125345.0,
      "text": "the solar wind is sometimes affected by solar storms"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 125370.0,
      "end_time": 128545.0,
      "text": "that I like to call \"space hurricanes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129687.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131640.0,
      "text": "When they arrive at planets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 131664.0,
      "end_time": 133888.0,
      "text": "they can perturb the space environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133913.0,
      "end_time": 137198.0,
      "text": "which in turn creates the northern or southern lights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137222.0,
      "end_time": 139410.0,
      "text": "for example, here on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139434.0,
      "end_time": 141302.0,
      "text": "but also Saturn"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141953.0,
      "end_time": 143906.0,
      "text": "and also Jupiter."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145151.0,
      "end_time": 147839.0,
      "text": "Luckily, here on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147863.0,
      "end_time": 150954.0,
      "text": "we are protected by our planet&#39;s natural shield,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150978.0,
      "end_time": 154890.0,
      "text": "a magnetic bubble that we call the magnetosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154113.0,
      "end_time": 156491.0,
      "text": "and that you can see here on the right side."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 157281.0,
      "end_time": 160529.0,
      "text": "Nonetheless, solar storms can still be responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160553.0,
      "end_time": 165167.0,
      "text": "for disrupting satellite telecommunications and operations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 165191.0,
      "end_time": 168796.0,
      "text": "for disrupting navigation systems, such as GPS,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168820.0,
      "end_time": 171301.0,
      "text": "as well as electric power transmission."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 171895.0,
      "end_time": 177749.0,
      "text": "All of these are technologies on which us humans rely more and more."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178420.0,
      "end_time": 182882.0,
      "text": "I mean, imagine if you woke up tomorrow without a working cell phone --"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 183692.0,
      "end_time": 185245.0,
      "text": "no internet on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 185269.0,
      "end_time": 187775.0,
      "text": "which means no social media."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 187799.0,
      "end_time": 190723.0,
      "text": "I mean, to me that would be worse than the zombie apocalypse."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 190747.0,
      "end_time": 191955.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 192605.0,
      "end_time": 194700.0,
      "text": "By constantly monitoring the Sun, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 194724.0,
      "end_time": 197114.0,
      "text": "we now know where the solar storms come from."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 197753.0,
      "end_time": 199697.0,
      "text": "They come from regions of the Sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 199722.0,
      "end_time": 203140.0,
      "text": "where a tremendous amount of energy is being stored."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 203380.0,
      "end_time": 204550.0,
      "text": "You have an example here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204574.0,
      "end_time": 208384.0,
      "text": "as a complex structure hanging above the solar surface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208408.0,
      "end_time": 210828.0,
      "text": "just on the verge of erupting."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 211877.0,
      "end_time": 214763.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, we cannot send probes"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 214787.0,
      "end_time": 218206.0,
      "text": "in the scorching hot atmosphere of the Sun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 218230.0,
      "end_time": 223438.0,
      "text": "where temperatures can rise up to around 10 million degrees Kelvin."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 224227.0,
      "end_time": 228438.0,
      "text": "So what I do is I use computer simulations"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228462.0,
      "end_time": 233295.0,
      "text": "in order to analyze but also to predict the behavior of these storms"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 233319.0,
      "end_time": 236100.0,
      "text": "when they&#39;re just born at the Sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 237421.0,
      "end_time": 240180.0,
      "text": "This is only one part of the story, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 241486.0,
      "end_time": 245344.0,
      "text": "When these solar storms are moving in space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 245368.0,
      "end_time": 248974.0,
      "text": "some of them will inevitably encounter space probes"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 248998.0,
      "end_time": 253606.0,
      "text": "that we humans have sent in order to explore other worlds."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 254105.0,
      "end_time": 256938.0,
      "text": "What I mean by other worlds is, for example, planets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 256962.0,
      "end_time": 259620.0,
      "text": "such as Venus or Mercury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 259860.0,
      "end_time": 261806.0,
      "text": "but also objects, such as comets."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 262584.0,
      "end_time": 265170.0,
      "text": "And while these space probes have been made"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 265194.0,
      "end_time": 267905.0,
      "text": "for different scientific endeavors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 267929.0,
      "end_time": 273660.0,
      "text": "they can also act like tiny cosmic meteorological stations"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273900.0,
      "end_time": 276820.0,
      "text": "and monitor the evolution of these space storms."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 276979.0,
      "end_time": 282313.0,
      "text": "So I, with a group of researchers, gather and analyze this data"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 282338.0,
      "end_time": 285387.0,
      "text": "coming from different locations of the Solar System."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 285411.0,
      "end_time": 288727.0,
      "text": "And by doing so, my research shows that, actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 288751.0,
      "end_time": 290839.0,
      "text": "solar storms have a generic shape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 290863.0,
      "end_time": 295368.0,
      "text": "and that this shape evolves as solar storms move away from the Sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 295392.0,
      "end_time": 296546.0,
      "text": "And you know what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 296571.0,
      "end_time": 301904.0,
      "text": "This is key for building tools to predict space weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 303420.0,
      "end_time": 306505.0,
      "text": "I would like to leave you with this beautiful image."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 306529.0,
      "end_time": 308938.0,
      "text": "This is us here on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 309692.0,
      "end_time": 311900.0,
      "text": "this pale blue dot."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 311736.0,
      "end_time": 315400.0,
      "text": "And while I study the Sun and its storms every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 315424.0,
      "end_time": 319349.0,
      "text": "I will always have a deep love for this beautiful planet --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 320760.0,
      "end_time": 321467.0,
      "text": "a pale blue dot indeed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 321491.0,
      "end_time": 325375.0,
      "text": "but a pale blue dot with an invisible magnetic shield"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 325399.0,
      "end_time": 327605.0,
      "text": "that helps to protect us."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 327629.0,
      "end_time": 328935.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 328959.0,
      "end_time": 332300.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}